data.description: Great opportunity to own this split-level home, with good size sf. 3 standard bedrooms. Also, one full and quarter bath. Nice wood flooring. Beautiful kitchen with granite countertops, finished walk out basement and 2 attached garage makes this house more convenient. Beautiful bathrooms. The property is well maintained a new roof in 2022, new deck in 2023. You will love this new patio in the back yard for family and friend reunions, you can spend a lot of time in the nice back yard as is very private with a fence. Nice south side location and an awesome neighborhood complement the house.
